Summary of a prevR object.

Source: R/show.prevR.r
show-prevR-method.Rd

Method show for objects of class prevR: shows a summary of the object's characteristics.

# S4 method for prevR
show(object)

Arguments

object

object of class prevR.

Note

Exactly the same as print().

See also

summary().

Examples

fdhs

#> 
#> Boundary coordinate range
#>         min       max

#> y  4.736723 15.082593
